         <abstract>
            <p>
               Collection of texts used for the funeral service and the preparation of the body for the burial. It is also supposed to grant forgiveness to the sins of the dead.
               The time of the composition of the work is unknown. The oldest extant manuscripts date to the 15th century.
            </p>
         </abstract>
